trans-unit.source: Provides a thread-safe list of <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma lista thread-safe de objetos <see cref="T:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> list is used to specify the output listeners for the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> collections.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> lista é usada para especificar os ouvintes de saída para o <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> e <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> coleções.

trans-unit.source: You cannot create an instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: Não é possível criar uma instância dessa classe.

trans-unit.source: This list is thread-safe, however the methods used to access the list and the enumerator do not take synchronization locks.
trans-unit.target: Essa lista é thread-safe, no entanto, os métodos usados para acessar a lista e o enumerador não usem bloqueios de sincronização.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the collection is copied, the copy is modified, and a reference is set to the copy of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Em vez disso, a coleção é copiada, a cópia é modificada e uma referência está definido para a cópia da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Methods like <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A> modify the elements in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Métodos como <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>, e <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A> modificar os elementos na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> class provides the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Count%2A> property for information about the list.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> classe fornece a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Count%2A> propriedade para obter informações sobre a lista.

trans-unit.source: It also provides the following methods: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Contains%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.IndexOf%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Ele também fornece os seguintes métodos: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Contains%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.IndexOf%2A>.

trans-unit.source: This class also provides the following methods to modify the list: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Insert%2A>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe também fornece os seguintes métodos para modificar a lista: <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Insert%2A>, e <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.CopyTo%2A> method copies a part of the list to an array.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.CopyTo%2A> método copia uma parte da lista em uma matriz.

trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.RemoveAt%2A> método exclui o membro da lista em um número de índice especificado.
